text: Shailendra Khanal was in the Armed Police Force of Nepal. He was the 10th Inspector General of the Armed Police Force (Nepal). ==Early life== Khanal was born in Kathmandu, Nepal. ==Career== Khanal worked in the Nepal Armed police force for 30 years. In April 2018, government appointed him as the 10th Inspector General of the Armed Police Force of Nepal. In April 2022, he retired from the Armed Police Force after his term as Inspector General ended. ==References== ==Other websites== * Armed Police Force, Nepal Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Nepalese people
